Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:34.51,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Thread
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lion King Touji Souya\Nversus Kai Shimada 8th-Dan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}20th Lion King Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is the right place, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:50.77,RightSignL2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hesitant\N17-year-old
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a huge hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:02:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey! Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Nikaidou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Brother’s being interviewed\Nby reporters in the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This is the 20th anniversary, so on the eve\Ntonight, there's also a fan gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It must be hard on Brother and the others,\Nwith the matches starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The fan gathering is from three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Once it starts, sit as close as you can\Nto Brother in the Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We have nothing to do with this,\Nso to sit by him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Nothing to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We're in the same workshop!\NPlus I'm his "little brother" disciple!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}When he's surrounded\Nby all of these unfamiliar people
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}and steeling himself, I want to support him\Nso he's not worn out before the first match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a relief to see a familiar face, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And, Brother is usually\Nvery considerate towards others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Hadn't thought it\Nthrough that far
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nikaidou, are you...\Nactually more mature than me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's good to experience this atmosphere\Nand get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That way, when the time comes,\NI won't get too excited and lose my focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When what time comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it's my turn to play\Nin the title match, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Blunt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You said that matter-of-factly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Like it's a matter of course!\NRight now, we're still C-1 and C-2!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Lion King Tournament First Match\NTournament Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have my shot at the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't think that, how could I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikaidou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I saw Nikaidou's face as he said that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and was shaken considerably.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you back at the Hall around three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While I was running in circles getting lost,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my peer has already hardened his resolve.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should tell you if I ran into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your tournament prize money\Nand match earnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from living expenses,\Nyou've been depositing it in my bank account.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, maybe you think of it as payment\Nfor taking care of you all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no need to think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... I can't just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Kouda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You hang on to the kid's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If a kid had a small fortune at his disposal,\Nhe'll just blow it on unsavory things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman, Rei isn't that kind of boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So more than not being the type, a boy\Nhis age can't blow money on those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:57.29,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sake
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:57.29,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cigarettes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:57.29,OnTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Questionable\NPubs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:57.29,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gambling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.29,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOPE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poor kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's got all this money,\Nbut nothing to spend it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could support a selfish girlfriend at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about that angle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama-wama! Little guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman, please go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, like the chairman said, I'll hold on\Nto your money until you come of age,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but if you ever need it, just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is Kyouko doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently she often stays over with you,\Nbut is she giving you any trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is he talking about?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So she hasn't been going to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what she's thinking anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad. Sis is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kouda 8th-Dan! Kiriyama 5th-Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, do you mind if I get a few pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do? Should I tell him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if my adoptive father finds out, he'll...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And what will happen to my adoptive sister?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Is there anything that I can do right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What an incredible garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe a hotel in the city\Nhas a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do they always pass each other by?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:07:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though neither one of them\Nwants to sever the relationship...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sun shower...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Souya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, Souya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Souya! You numbskull!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man of the hour,\NI was wondering where you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you! You're soaked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you were with him,\Nyou should've brought him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go. You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, with the event starting, this is not where\Nthe main draw is supposed to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That took my breath away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't sense him there at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment I laid eyes on him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}all the sound in the world vanished.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His appearance hasn't changed at all.\NIt's almost like time stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:25.38,CenterSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"He isn't human"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somebody whispered\Nin the depths of my memory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment he left...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the sky broke open and heavy rain\Nbegan pouring down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}He's going up against that person...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:42.98,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Thread
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Mr. Shimada...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:46.98,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Water's Surface
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a strange sight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When he entered the Hall,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the room went silent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}The crowd parted for him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sorry, everyone. Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Turns out he was in the garden,\Njust gazing at the carp, all care-free!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Unbelievable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well, shall we get started?\NCome on, Souya, to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He became a professional at 15,\Nwhile still in middle school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At 21, he became\Nthe youngest shogi master in history.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, he overthrew\None record after another in the shogi world,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and in the first time in history,\Nhe won all seven major titles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then ten-odd years passed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He continued to reign on the throne,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his appearance still unchanging.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never fading, never tiring,\Nnever becoming corrupted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With overwhelming power,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he quietly continues to reside at the top.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He could be compared to a god, however,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}someone once said,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the devil has the same kind of face."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's continue with Shimada 8th-Dan,\Nif you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to thank all the fans for\Ncoming here, despite it being a weeknight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About three weeks have passed\Nsince I became the challenger,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but the days have just flown by...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}At the end of the night\Nbefore the first match, Mr. Shimada said,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I need two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to beat that monster twice\Nand get two white stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I'll never get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}20th Lion King Tournament Schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sixth match...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Sixth Match\NApril 9-10 Tendou (Yamagata Prefecture)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Kai Shimada, 8th dan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}The Lion King Tournament,\Na seven-match showdown.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}After 114 moves, he conceded the first match.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You snitched on me to Dad, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My answer is the same from my email.\NI didn't tell him anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He put a stop on my credit card,\Nand he's bombarding me with questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?\NThis is all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I didn't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, you brought it all on yourself, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I brought it on myself?\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking down at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All you do is whine pitifully\Nand play messy shogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:12:01.18,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shiver Shiver\NShake Shake
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Shiver\NShiver
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akari, u-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us. Please, as you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-A fight? Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will he get bullied?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's too bad, but he was evidently\Nin the middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}A witch? Is she a witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It can't be helped. Let's go home\Nand eat the inari sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Still, it seems Rei sure is dealing with\Na strong-willed girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Who are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}From the neighborhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}They've done a lot for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the next home, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You put on the "woe-is-me" act again,\Nand won them over?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going in to another house\Nand messing up another family?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nasty piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so irritated that my heart's beating fast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei's expression was white like a stone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've never seen him look like that before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And also...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he didn't even look...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in our direction!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, eat these!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis and I made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty of egg and sesame seeds in them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and they're sweet and really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eating them will cheer you up,\Nso you better eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:15.64,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grrrr...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Middle School Student
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let's go, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What was with her? I'm so pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That woman is definitely bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Come on now, Hina. Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Don't say things like "pissed" okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is the witch gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Rei, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he just take it\Nand not say anything back?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I do agree with you. A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A little. Just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:56.02,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Water's Surface
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:15:00.02,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Base of the Blue Night
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? So sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fried wrapping is too sweet!\NIt's not candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this one has minced pickled wasabi in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! When the flavors change,\NI can't stop eating them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I get fat, somebody will be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You follow me home, eat my food,\Nand then complain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And vegetables in the second layer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Simmered chicken and vegetables?\NOld hags!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that's a hard sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like, "See how domestic I am?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like, "This is just what a boy\Nliving on his own hankers for, isn't it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So there's okra and broccoli...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boiled with sesame oil and salt...\NKorean-style seasonings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:01.75,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crunch\NCrunch
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.04,OnTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Munch\NMunch
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:04.42,OnTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lick
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, you'd better be getting home.\NMom probably has dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My skirt is too tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I-It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Now that I'm full, I feel sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Rei, let me borrow your clothes.\NDo you have any sweatshirts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Didn't Dad just get mad at you?\NGo home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shut up already. Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'll just call them later, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Don't go digging around opening stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Toss\NToss
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Toss
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.75,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Swish
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I finally feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, which girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The middle-schooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not the housewife, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The housewife...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're referring to Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So her name's Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was carrying her little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}W-Witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those three are sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:22.91,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These Three
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, I don't think Akari\Nis that much older than you, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The middle-schooler or the old wo...\Nthe oldest sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which? Why would you think it'd be like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's neither of them.\NDid you call her an "old wo..."?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, don't tell me it's the kindergartener.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, just go home already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at Rei's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a problem\Nif I'm really at Rei's place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that, the last train is long gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, what the hell?\NWhy can't he trust his own daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Grr\NGrrrr
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't understand Kyouko anymore!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, me neither.\NWe sure agree on that sense, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's always out of sync about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "If you have a boyfriend\Nwho's taking care of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then bring him to the house\Nso I can meet him."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The man's 20 years older than me, married...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and on top of that,\Nhe was Dad's former disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can bring him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you choose a guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\NI want to ask myself the same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That munchkin called me a "witch."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I really were a witch,\NI wouldn't have such pathetic hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Rei. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the darkness of that night,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the glow from her phone's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}small LCD screen faintly lit up her silhouette{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}over and over and over again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I watched it quietly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The room was dyed blue,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as if we were at the bottom of the sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It felt like all we did was sink that night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When she said, "Well, see you around,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I started to say "Yeah," but then clammed up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Even though I felt torn that day\Nwhen I left that house,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}for my older sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}...and me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}nothing has changed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}And without being able to change,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}we also haven't been able to become\Nsiblings nor remain strangers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did you run here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I was on cleaning duty\Nand it ran long...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:21:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Cleaning duty." Huh. I haven't\Nheard that word in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That phrase brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You really are still a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get inside already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikaidou has been waiting impatiently\Nfor your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won the final match!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll be Rank C-1 next term,\Nthe same level as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice it too loud. And that attitude, too.\NIt annoys the hell out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Shigeta, congratulations\Non retaining your rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My heart was throbbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was close\Nto being in the same rank as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? What were you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which shogi world did you get\Nthat information from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was confident this season,\Nso you got any complaints?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's good that no one\Ngot any bad news this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to hold on\Nto my Rank A this season, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although, how can I put it? I squeaked by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was on the borderline and made it by a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Made it by a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When Brother says that, it has weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I sincerely congratulate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NWhy are you guys covering your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I finally caught up to you, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'll be waiting for the day\Nwhen we have a match together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.71,0:22:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Right, rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.06,0:22:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Nikaidou said that to me,\Nhis face shone so bright that I had to squint,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.64,0:22:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and in my eyelids,\NI saw that morning's river surface.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.73,0:22:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll turn 18 next month.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.98,0:22:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}And I'll become a 2nd year\Nhigh school student, one year behind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without being able to change anything...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a new spring will come.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Base of the Blue Night
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:37.39,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 18
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.35,0:24:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you free tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.89,0:24:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then do you want to go?\NTo Mouseland?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.60,0:24:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just us two guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.98,0:24:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how can I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.90,0:24:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would feel creepy or like...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.07,0:24:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watch the next episode of\N"March Comes in Like a Lion", please!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.70,0:24:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, my passionate battle\Nwith you is just beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.58,0:24:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, my rival!
